Live version from "I Might Be Wrong: Live Recordings"

version_description: Thumb on the low E string creates a nice bass progression for Adim/F# Asus4/F and D/F#.
This version attempts to account for all the little variations Thom does when playing this, and add accuracy. Shoutout to versions one and three which I used as a guide.
The others versions miss a lot of things, like the variation, the complex chords. this is a complet version accurate from the studio version. Take a lot from the V2 guitar pro.
